{"id":104,"ayahs":[{"number":163,"arabic":"۞ إِنَّآ أَوْحَيْنَآ إِلَيْكَ كَمَآ أَوْحَيْنَآ إِلَىٰ نُوحٍۢ وَٱلنَّبِيِّۦنَ مِنۢ بَعْدِهِۦ ۚ وَأَوْحَيْنَآ إِلَىٰٓ إِبْرَٰهِيمَ وَإِسْمَٰعِيلَ وَإِسْحَٰقَ وَيَعْقُوبَ وَٱلْأَسْبَاطِ وَعِيسَىٰ وَأَيُّوبَ وَيُونُسَ وَهَٰرُونَ وَسُلَيْمَٰنَ ۚ وَءَاتَيْنَا دَاوُۥدَ زَبُورًۭا","translation":"BEHOLD, We have inspired thee [O Prophet] just as We inspired Noah and all the prophets after him - as We inspired Abraham, and Ishmael, and Isaac, and Jacob, and their descendants, including Jesus and Job, and Jonah, and Aaron, and Solomon; and as We vouchsafed unto David a book of divine wisdom;","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/656.mp3","surahId":4,"words":[{"id":82068,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ إِنَّآ","translation":"(হে নবী) আমরা নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/004_163_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82069,"position":2,"arabic":"أَوْحَيْنَآ","translation":"আমরা ওহী পাঠিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/004_163_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82070,"position":3,"arabic":"إِلَيْكَ","translation":"তোমার প্রতি","audioUrl":"wbw/004_163_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82071,"position":4,"arabic":"كَمَآ","translation":"যেমন","audioUrl":"wbw/004_163_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82072,"position":5,"arabic":"أَوْحَيْنَآ","translation":"আমরা ওহী পাঠিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/004_163_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82073,"position":6,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","translation":"প্রতি","audioUrl":"wbw/004_163_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82074,"position":7,"arabic":"نُوحٍۢ","translation":"নূহের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_163_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82075,"position":8,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّبِيِّـۧنَ","translation":"ও নবীদের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_163_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82076,"position":9,"arabic":"مِنۢ","translation":"পরে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_163_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":82077,"position":10,"arabic":"بَعْدِهِۦ ۚ","translation":"তার","audioUrl":"wbw/004_163_011.mp3","charTy